            </div>
            <p class="about-lead">It keeps not only finished knowledge, but also work-in-progress thinking, failed attempts, and changed decisions.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section about-reveal">
            <h3>Current Direction</h3>
            <p class="about-lead">What I want to build is not simply more code.</p>
            <blockquote class="about-quote">
                <strong>An environment where knowledge accumulates automatically during development, AI understands that knowledge, and people and AI solve the next problem together &mdash; faster and more accurately.</strong>
            </blockquote>
            <p class="about-lead">That is my current direction.</p>
        </section>

